                  a.abouttext(href="https://twitter.com/LinuxBiscuit") Twitter
                li
                  i.fa.fa-facebook.fa-2x
                  a.abouttext(href="https://www.facebook.com/linuxbiscuit") Facebook
            div.large-6.columns
              ul.tabs(data-tab)
                li.tab-title.active
                  a(href="#whoami") Who am I?
                li.tab-title
                  a(href="#interests") Interests
                li.tab-title
                  a(href="#work") Work
              div.tabs-content
                div.content.active#whoami
                  p I am currently a student at the University of Canterbury studying Computer Science. I am interested in many areas or computers science like Web development, game development, software engineering, networking etc.
